      <div class = "title">Design</div>
      <p>We decided to implement the Tinder style swiping into a carousel at the top of our main page. This way, users
        had the option to quickly choose a location based on pictures. On top of listing each "spot" in the Instgram style,
        we also implemented a visual map to help users better locate locations.
      </p>
